{"tid":2075893,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"英國央行行長：若央行不干預 英國3月份已面臨破產","createTime":"2020-06-23T06:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:26:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6cf27a93256787ae73952944d778262883b3d6","tid":2075893,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"2020/06/23 11:46    <br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）重創全球經濟，英國央行英格蘭銀行（Bank of England）行長貝利（Andrew Bailey）坦言，英國在疫情爆發初期，已接近有效破產。<br />\n<br />\n........<br />\n<br />\n英國政府的債券管理辦公室向國際投資者出售債券，該辦公室4月份時表示，計劃在短短4個月內從債券市場投資者籌集2250億英鎊，為疫情期間大幅增長的公共支出提供資金。<br />\n<br />\n........<br />\n<br />\n此外，貝利暗示，未來在取消緊急刺激措施時，將以縮表為首要目標，而後才升息，並強調此舉將為央行挹注更多火力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3206236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3206236&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7q0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=c45b7e63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3206236&h=dc85ffd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3206236</a>"},{"pid":"7309cad51294e2187ed06b6e253a21ece3993d97","tid":2075893,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"幾時支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbabe3cb7a6a1e9ddfb5c8c14633068f2c636f2","tid":2075893,"uid":24024,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7309cad51294e2187ed06b6e253a21ece3993d97","tid":2075893,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"幾時支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"美爆英爆都未到支爆啦<br />\n<br />\n支那最撚癲係可以公開抄富豪家<br />\n一個月抄一個都夠頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民又夠聽話<br />\n整多次全民大煉鋼都仲得啊"},{"pid":"4b0c92937bae97d